            <ab>[- - -] (11 lines too fragmentary to be translated);For there is no one else in Philadelphia to whom those who are wronged can flee for protection at any time. Know therefore that through no other person can I too be cleared of the charge unjustly brought against me. For there is no ground for it, but the charge is trifling, so that with the gods' help I am of good hope that I shall be saved. But Kraton is not in the same case; for from his deeds, by the genius of the king [- - -]</ab>
